span>单理<span class="_ _8"></span>解为<span class="_ _8"></span>“宿<span class="_ _8"></span>命论<span class="_ _8"></span>”<span class="_ _b"></span>，<span class="_ _8"></span>完全<span class="_ _8"></span>取决<span class="_ _8"></span>于前<span class="_ _8"></span>世，<span class="_ _8"></span>这不<span class="_ _8"></span>是对业<span class="_ _8"></span>的</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ye7 ff10 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">正确认识。<span class="_ _1"></span>真实的情况是：<span class="_ _5"></span>我们今天所感受到的一切，<span class="_ _1"></span>有一</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ye8 ff10 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">部分的确是前世的业导致的，<span class="_ _6"></span>但也有一部分跟今生的因缘有</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ye9 ff10 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">关，了解到这点，你就明白断恶修善的意义了。 </div><div class="t m0 x21 h4 y6e ff10 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">说得明确一点，相信业因果，也是一种智慧。 </div><div class="t m0 x21 h4 y39 ff10 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">我常常觉得，<span class="_ _1"></span>学习是一件乐事，<span class="_ _5"></span>尤其是学习利他。<span class="_ _1"></span>佛教</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
